data.meta_description: This tRNA sequence is 74 nucleotides long and is found in Callicarpa longifolia var. floccosa. Annotated by 1 database (ENA). Has a conserved secondary structure or a structured region. Matches 1 Rfam family (tRNA, RF00005). Callicarpa longifolia var. floccosa tRNA-Pro sequence is a product of trnP-UGG gene.
